- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes extensions to the Recurrent Neural Aligner model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with a neural network model for speech recognition. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with processing of speech signals.
